|               |                               Filter: hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderdate >= Date32("1995-01-01") AND hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderdate <= Date32("1996-12-31")                                                                                                                         |
|               |                                 TableScan: hadoop.tpch.orders projection=[o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderdate], partial_filters=[hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderdate >= Date32("1995-01-01"), hadoop.tpch.orders.o_orderdate <= Date32("1996-12-31")]                                 |
